Modules¶

Module that contains tools for passing VoightKampff test.

class voight_kampff.VoightKampff(file_path: str)¶

Bases: object

Test used by the LAPD’s Blade Runners to assist in determining whether or not an individual was a replicant.

__init__(file_path: str) → None¶

Initialize a VoightKampff class that helps to reveal repliacnt

Parameters:

file_path (str) – Path to a JSON file with questions for test.

__weakref__¶

list of weak references to the object (if defined)

replicant_test() → bool¶

The test itself. You need to write four biological parameters for each answer. Amount of questions is at least 10.

class valid_params.BiologicalParametres(*, respiration: int, heart_rate: int, blushing_level: int, pupillary_dilation: int)¶

Bases: BaseModel

Restrain from adding unnormal biological params

Parameters:

  • respiration (int) – Amount of breathes in and osygen per minute.

  • heart_rate – Number of contractions of the heart per minute.

  • blushing_level (int) – Degree of reddening of a person’s face.

  • pupillary_dilation (int) – Current pupil size.
